📘 PAYLAŞTIKÇA | Bilgi Paylaştıkça Çoğalır!
This is a responsive website project built using HTML, CSS, JavaScript, and Bootstrap. The theme of the website revolves around sharing knowledge — as the title says: "Bilgi Paylaştıkça Çoğalır!" (Knowledge multiplies as it's shared).

🎯 Features
🌐 Responsive Layout: Optimized for all screen sizes (desktop, tablet, and mobile).

🧭 Navigation Bar: Sticky top navigation with links to key sections: Home, About, Team, Gallery, and Contact.

🖼️ Image Carousel: Full-width image slider to display visuals in an engaging way.

👥 Team Section: Introduces team members professionally (not visible in GIF but implied by nav link).

🖼️ Gallery Section: Placeholder for displaying images (if implemented).

📞 Contact Section: Allows users to get in touch (if implemented).

🛠️ Technologies Used
HTML5

CSS3 / SCSS

JavaScript

Bootstrap 5

